{"tid":2198497,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"證監會：已準備好配合黨軍切生豬肉行動","createTime":"2020-09-11T11:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T12:36:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc89135d69ab4bd6ab2ea84ff82666ad5166b27","tid":2198497,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"證監會準備就警方調查壹傳媒股份提供協助<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日拘捕15人，涉嫌操控壹傳媒股價。證監會晚上發出聲明，指由於調查仍在進行，不適合就案件作進一步評論，已準備好回應警方針對《證券及期貨條例》所載任何潛在罪行而提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n證監會指，根據警方與證監會的諒解備忘錄，雙方承諾盡最大可能合作，以有效執行與證券和期貨有關的犯罪或非法活動的監管和執法職能。對於市場行為不當犯罪，例如虛假交易的調查，通常涉及複雜的法律和證據問題，以及涉及證券市場功能，交易方法和投資者行為的專家評估的需求。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2356814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2356814&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fr500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=79361c24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2356814</a>"},{"pid":"b1eea782a46d73194d8b03968688db8c72c40f82","tid":2198497,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}